OL,3,CShocking moment police find Constance
OL,4,CMarten's baby in rubbish-filled bag
OL,6,FThe horrifying moment a missing baby
OL,7,Fgirl was found dead amid rubbish
OL,8,Fstuffed inside a Lidl supermarket bag
OL,9,Fhas been shown during the trial of
OL,10,Fwealthy aristocrat Constance Marten
OL,11,Fand her partner Mark Gordon.
OL,13,FMarten, 36, and Gordon, 49, refused to
OL,14,Ftell police where their daughter
OL,15,FVictoria was after the to Brighton,
OL,16,FEast Sussex.
OL,18,FDays later, police made the grim
OL,19,Fdiscovery of the child's remains in a
OL,20,Fdisused shed on an allotment near to
OL,21,Fwhere they had been detained.
