OL,3,CShocking moment police find Constance
OL,4,CMarten's baby in rubbish-filled bag
OL,6,FOn Wednesday, the defendants sat in
OL,7,Fthe Old Bailey dock as police body-
OL,8,Fworn video was played of the moment
OL,9,Fbaby Victoria was finally found on the
OL,10,Fafternoon of 1 March last year.
OL,12,FOfficers were seen in the footage
OL,13,Fcarefully probing the large red
OL,14,Fshopping bag which had been placed on
OL,15,Fthe decking outside the shed on Lower
OL,16,FRoedale Allotments.
OL,18,FThey were seen pulling out pieces of
OL,19,Frubbish to reveal the baby, whose body
OL,20,Fwas blocked out on the video.
