OL,3,CShocking moment police find Constance
OL,4,CMarten's baby in rubbish-filled bag
OL,6,FPC Allen Ralph, who had been sent from
OL,7,FScotland Yard to help in the search,
OL,8,Ftold jurors he had already seen
OL,9,Fearlier CCTV footage of the
OL,10,Fdistinctive Lidl bag before he was
OL,11,Fdeployed with a colleague to search
OL,12,Fthe allotments.
OL,14,FAs he approached the disused shed, he
OL,15,Fnoticed a broken window and lifted the
OL,16,Fdoor to get in.
OL,18,FThe first thing he noticed was the
OL,19,Fsmell, he said: "I remember saying
OL,20,F'either something is dead in there or
OL,21,Fsomething has died'."
