OL,6,FInside there was a tent, out-of-date
OL,7,Fmilk and bread on a makeshift table
OL,8,Fand the shopping bag underneath, he
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,FDuring a break, PC Ralph told his
OL,12,Fpartner he was sure he had seen the
OL,13,Fbag before so they went back to take a
OL,14,Fcloser look.
OL,16,FHe told jurors: "I lifted it and it
OL,17,Fwas heavy and there was no reason for
OL,18,Fit to be heavy from what I could see
OL,19,Finside.
