OL,3,CShocking moment police find Constance
OL,4,CMarten's baby in rubbish-filled bag
OL,6,F"I remember quite clearly there was
OL,7,Fjust a lot of rubbish."
OL,9,FPC Ralph said there were two baby
OL,10,Fnappies, a pink baby blanket, drinks
OL,11,Fcans, cardboard, leaves and other
OL,12,Fpieces of rubbish.
OL,14,FThe officer said he put on gloves
OL,15,Fbefore placing the bag on the decking
OL,16,Foutside the shed to examine the
OL,17,Fcontents.
OL,19,FAs they searched, his colleague
OL,20,Findicated that he had seen what looked
OL,21,Flike the head of a doll, jurors heard.
