OL,6,FPC Ralph said the baby was "very pale"
OL,7,Fand "very cold" to the touch.
OL,9,Ffor the missing baby, the defendants
OL,10,Ftravelled across England and ended up
OL,11,Fliving off-grid in a tent on the South
OL,12,FDowns for around seven weeks, jurors
OL,13,Fhave heard.
OL,15,FOn 20 February last year, they were
OL,16,Fcaught on CCTV footage carrying a Lidl
OL,17,Fbag and rummaging through bins outside
OL,18,FHollingbury Golf Club in Brighton.
