OL,3,CShocking moment police find Constance
OL,4,CMarten's baby in rubbish-filled bag
OL,6,FSeven days later, they were arrested
OL,7,Fon suspicion of child neglect after a
OL,8,Fmember of the public spotted them and
OL,9,Fcalled 999.
OL,11,FThe defendants were taken to separate
OL,12,Fpolice stations and repeatedly refused
OL,13,Fto answer questions about the missing
OL,14,Fchild.
OL,16,FJurors were shown photographs of
OL,17,FMarten looking dishevelled and with
OL,18,Ffurniture stuffing coming out of her
OL,19,Fclothes.
