OL,6,FProsecutor Joel Smith told the court:
OL,7,F"The police still did not know where
OL,8,Fthe child was, whether the child was
OL,9,Falive or dead or even the sex of the
OL,10,Fchild."
OL,12,FAt Brighton Police station, Marten
OL,13,Ftold officers: "I'm sorry I haven't
OL,14,Featen or slept for a long time. I need
OL,15,Fto get some sleep before I can make a
OL,16,Fproper decision."
OL,18,FShe went on to answer "no comment" to
OL,19,Fall questions she was asked.
