OL,6,F"I'm entitled to respect....I'm in
OL,7,Fcustody but that doesn't mean I'm a
OL,8,Fdog."
OL,10,FGordon asked for pills and said he was
OL,11,Fin "distress" before adding: "I am the
OL,12,Fdetainee.
OL,14,F"You can't just take my rights around
OL,15,Fme ... lock me up and say ah we don't
OL,16,Fcare about your feet, you're fine,
OL,17,Fjust go ahead and get interviewed.
OL,19,F"I feel like I'm scum. I feel like I'm
OL,20,Fscumbag actually.
