OL,6,F"I feel like I'm a piece of s**t. I
OL,7,Ffeel like that's how I've been
OL,8,Ftreated."
OL,10,FOn being told by an officer that the
OL,11,F"main concerns" were for the baby,
OL,12,FGordon continued to complain of pain.
OL,14,FAn officer said: "I want to ask one
OL,15,Fquestion."
OL,17,FGordon replied: "What?"
OL,19,FThe officer asked: "What was the
OL,20,Fbaby's name?"
